Next, I zero in on "Phường Hồng Châu" within "Tỉnh Hưng Yên." Based on resolution 1666/NQ-UBTVQH15 and the "New wards" data, it's clear that the old "Phường Hồng Châu" is now part of the new "Phường Hồng Châu." The name has been retained, although it's the result of a merger. This direct mapping gives me high confidence in the output. The address "Phường Hồng Châu, Thành phố Hưng Yên, Tỉnh Hưng Yên" still resolves to "Phường Hồng Châu, Thành phố Hưng Yên, Tỉnh Hưng Yên", with high confidence, based on the mentioned resolution and the new ward data.
